*3.4 Supplier Details*

Purpose: Drill-down view for a single supplier — profile info, categories/products they offer, and contact/communication actions.

**Regions:**
1. `<AppHeader />` (toolbar variant: search, hamburger, avatar)
2. **Profile + actions row:**
   - `profile` pill button (left) — supplier name/avatar entry point, likely expands to full profile info
   - Right-aligned stacked action buttons: Add (`+`) and Message/Comment (speech bubble icon)
3. **Categories band** — centered "categories" label, flanked by two pill placeholders (left/right) — likely prev/next category navigation or tag chips
4. **Product/offering grid** — 3-column grid of `<ImagePlaceholderCard />` showing the products/items associated with this supplier (same card component as Suppliers grid, reused).

**React sketch:**
```
<SupplierDetailsPage>
  <AppHeader variant="toolbar" />
  <ProfileActionsRow>
    <ProfilePillButton />
    <ActionStack>
      <PrimaryButton icon="+" />
      <IconButton icon="message" />
    </ActionStack>
  </ProfileActionsRow>
  <CategoriesBand label="categories" />
  <ProductGrid>
    <ImagePlaceholderCard /> <ImagePlaceholderCard /> <ImagePlaceholderCard /> ...
  </ProductGrid>
</SupplierDetailsPage>
```

